criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. child age between 2- 5 years;

          2. child > 95th percentile BMI for age and sex 12, but not more than 100% above the mean
             BMI;

          3. medical clearance from pediatrician; and

          4. at least one parent with a BMI > 25. -

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. non-English speaking;

          2. living more than 50 miles from the medical center;

          3. a disability/illness that would preclude engagement in at least moderate physical
             activity;

          4. medical condition/medication associated with weight gain; or 5) enrolled in another
             weight control program.
